Variation.
Variation in scalation and body measurements of the type series is reported in Table 6 . Paratypes agree almost entirely with the holotype , with the exception of two male paratypes ( CAS 263529 ;
UF 187228
) that differ slightly in coloration, with both specimens having a darker dorsum with a more faded pattern, and speckled black on the gular region ( CAS 263529 )
.
